27/10/2002
BOROVETS, Bulgaria -- Royal families from European, Asian and African countries attended Saturday's (26 October) wedding of Princess Kalina, daughter of Bulgaria's ex-king and current Prime Minister Simeon Saxe-Coburg. 
The 30-year-old princess married 43-year-old Spanish sailor and researcher Kitin Munoz at the Borovetz ski resort. 
The ceremony enjoyed tremendous media interest, including live coverage on national TV and radio stations. 
The wedding was also seen as an attempt to boost Bulgaria's image as an attractive tourist destination. 
(BTA, BNT, bTV - 26/10/02)
